        <h2><span>SPONSOR A CHILD, AND GIVE THEM THE CHANCE TO GO TO SCHOOL</span></h2>
        <p>Children of the Mekong responds to the needs of the community. These needs differ from one region to another, and even from one child to another. This is why individual child sponsorship is an efficient, adapted and personalised solution.
        </br>
        </br>
        With £28 a month, the goal is to enable a child to go to school so that they can take charge of their future and that of their family.</p>
